                  </objectDesc>
                  <decoDesc>
                     <decoNote xml:id="d1">
                        <desc>Drawing of three figures, fol. 1r; Ḥarag, ff. 2r, 19v, 36r, 52r, 85v, 94v, 101v and 116v.</desc>
                     </decoNote>
                  </decoDesc>
                  <additions>
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">Genealogy of አቤቶ፡ ጊዮርጊስ and እሜቶ፡ ዮልያና, who descend from Emperor Dawit I, fol. 103v
                           
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">Names of original owners erased and sometimes replaced with ሕዝቅያስ and ኤልሳቤት, fol. 3r and throughout; Seal of the Institute of Ethiopian Studies, fol. 2r, 133v
                           
                        </item>
                     </list>
                  </additions>
                  <bindingDesc><binding><decoNote xml:id="b1">Stamped leather over wood boards; cloth between the pastedowns
                     
                  </decoNote></binding></bindingDesc>
               </physDesc>
               <history>
                  <origin>
